      "content": "### GET /user\n\n#### Overview\n\nFetches the profile information for the currently authenticated user, locating existing user data by the provided Bearer token.\n\n### API Endpoints\n\n* GET /user: Retrieve user profile information\n\n#### Request Requirements\n\n* Accept: application/json\n* Authorization: Bearer token\n* Content-Type: application/json\n\n### Response Specifications\n\n* HTTP Status Codes\n\t+ 200 OK: User profile information retrieved successfully\n\t+ 401 Unauthorized: Incorrect or missing authentication token\n\t+ 423 Locked: Requested resource is locked due to concurrent updates\n* Response Payload\n\t+ JSON object containing user profile information\n\t\t- Example structure:\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": 123,\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"join_date\": \"2022-01-01T00:00:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n#### User Profile Information\n\n| Field Name | Field Type | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| id | integer | Unique user identifier |\n| email | string | User-provided email address |\n| name | string | User-provided full name |\n| join_date | datetime | Date the user account",
